sudo apt-get install tint2
cd ~/.config/tint2

Modified the settings:
   1. Make panel size larger
      Change "panel_size = 100% 30" to "panel_size = 100% 64"
   2. Change the panel location
      Change "panel_position = bottom center horizontal" to "panel_position = top center horizontal"

Move the file and add symblic link so that we can track it using git hub
   1. move the config file to dotfiles folder
      mv tint2rc ~/dotfiles
   2. Add the symblic link for the file moved
      ln -s /home/charleszhang/dotfiles/tint2rc tint2rc
